      "title": "<span id=\"#53840\" class=\"scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold flex items-center\"><h1 class=\"inline !mb-1 scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold\">deliberately</h1><div class=\"pl-2 flex-1 text-textSecondary text-xl font-serif\">(adv.)</div></span>",
      "html": "<p>15世纪晚期，“经过考虑，有明确目的地”，来自 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of deliberate \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/deliberate\">deliberate</a>（形容词）+ <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of -ly \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/-ly\">-ly</a>（2）。</p>"
